{"tid":1011422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安員墮一米坑傷腳 警方列有人意外受傷處理","createTime":"2019-02-06T18:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T03:07:57.000Z","uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d44fb5a9d923ded0214b3689d81572a20e97bd91","tid":1011422,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T18:18:11.000Z","msg":"石硤尾白田白雲街1號地盤發生保安員墮坑意外，今日(6日)下午4時許，一名姓陳(62歲)男保安員，在上址地盤巡邏期間，未注意前面有坑，結果失足跌落一米深坑內，腳部受傷，姓潘(68歲)男主管發現報警。陳由到場消防員救起，救護員替他包紮後，將他送往明愛醫院治療。警方經初步調查，相信事件並無可疑，案件列有人意外受傷處理。"},{"pid":"674bc1f22b291c30c3eb757b67b951a03b7365e8","tid":1011422,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T18:28:11.000Z","msg":"窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d2a77f32824ec38e8419cb85d6c67ac7999d85","tid":1011422,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T18:29:10.000Z","msg":"大陸化了"},{"pid":"57f8a49b6283353742fce47d0a214f251e2e066c","tid":1011422,"uid":204728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"忍唔住笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}